WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.190 --> 00:00:04.850
Wake up your sweet tooth with the chocolate
for breakfast bar set that’s baconluxious.

00:00:04.850 --> 00:00:10.009
And write down your to do list on this piggy
bank made out of postit notes.

00:00:10.009 --> 00:00:14.719
Because it’s episode 49 of LÜT.

00:00:14.719 --> 00:00:20.550
Carry sun power on your back with a Voltaic
solar backpack. That features a solar panel

00:00:20.550 --> 00:00:25.930
and battery designed to transfer a few hours
in the sun into a fully-charged smartphone.

00:00:25.930 --> 00:00:30.500
And the fabric is made out of recycled soda
bottles with waterproof backing to protect

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:31.840
your devices.&nbsp;

00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:36.929
Devise some beats from your pants using a
pocket drum machine. Teenage Engineering’s

00:00:36.929 --> 00:00:42.110
pocket operators series features the battery
operated drum machine, bass synthesizer and

00:00:42.110 --> 00:00:47.539
a lead synthesizer. They each have 16 different
sounds and effects to make stuff on the go

00:00:47.539 --> 00:00:52.940
like this…

00:00:52.940 --> 00:00:59.250
Monitor the circadian rhythm of your newborn
thanks to the Mimo Smart Baby Monitor. A machine-washable

00:00:59.250 --> 00:01:05.030
onesie that tracks breathing, body position
and sleep status and sends the data to your

00:01:05.030 --> 00:01:10.180
smartphone so you can finally get a good night’s
sleep on your Ostrich arm pillow.

00:01:10.180 --> 00:01:16.110
The Valentine’s Day Mystery Box is filled
with I don’t know and neither will she!

00:01:16.110 --> 00:01:19.390
Or he. Or Cthulhu plush.

00:01:19.390 --> 00:01:24.140
Unicorn bouquet. That replaces roses with
the magical gift of unicorns each on their

00:01:24.140 --> 00:01:26.160
own stem that’s detachable.

00:01:26.160 --> 00:01:31.680
Attach these overly-complicated wooden light
switches that use gears, rack and pinion,

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:35.970
toggles and levers that are installed over
the existing plastic covers.&nbsp;

00:01:35.970 --> 00:01:39.990
Cover yourself and some friends with the world’s
largest underpants.&nbsp;

00:01:39.990 --> 00:01:45.320
And have the world’s most famous lake monster
stick its head out of pans when using the

00:01:45.320 --> 00:01:46.970
Nessie Ladle.

00:01:46.970 --> 00:01:49.130
Roller Tape.

00:01:49.130 --> 00:01:54.200
Clone your pets in the cuddliest way possible
by ordering a customized plush replica from

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:59.430
Cuddle Clones.com. Just upload some pictures
of your four-legged companion and in a few

00:01:59.430 --> 00:02:01.650
months you’ll have your stuffed Dragon.

00:02:01.650 --> 00:02:06.710
(Draggin’) around ice cold beverages is
easy with the IceMule. A portable cooler that

00:02:06.710 --> 00:02:12.460
keeps contents cold for up to 24 hours and
can be easily rolled up and stored when not

00:02:12.460 --> 00:02:13.540
in use.

00:02:13.540 --> 00:02:18.560
Use Key Kong to hold onto your keys so you
always know where they are.&nbsp;And all Key Kong

00:02:18.560 --> 00:02:20.490
asks for in return is...

00:02:20.490 --> 00:02:22.380
Just don’t take me for granite.

00:02:22.380 --> 00:02:27.460
The TextBlade doesn’t take touch-typing
for granted. At just one third the size and

00:02:27.460 --> 00:02:33.340
weight of an iPhone it provides the same full
finger spacing of a desktop and sets itself

00:02:33.340 --> 00:02:37.890
up magnetically. And the battery lasts about
a month per charge.&nbsp;

00:02:37.890 --> 00:02:42.230
Get medieval in your writing after having
a pen bestowed by a bowing knight.&nbsp;

00:02:42.230 --> 00:02:47.281
Or bring night into the future with the Leeo
Smart Alert Nightlight. Not only can you set

00:02:47.281 --> 00:02:51.459
its brightness and color it has an ambient
light setting to turn on when the lights get

00:02:51.459 --> 00:02:57.450
low. It listens for smoke alarm and carbon
monoxide alarms and monitors temperature and

00:02:57.450 --> 00:03:01.400
humidity and then alerts your smartphone&nbsp;if
anything is amiss.

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:06.070
Feel free to miss your mouth when wearing
a hydrophobic t-shirt from Threadsmiths. The

00:03:06.070 --> 00:03:12.040
100% cotton shirts contain no chemicals and
are crafted with a patented hydrophobic nanotechnology

00:03:12.040 --> 00:03:34.599
that repels water and dirt. And syrup. And
as always - thanks for watching.

